_:N8187fb23a76a48b0aafbad82a0dfb769 <http://schema.org/description> "The Health and Safety Executive (HSE) is Britain’s national regulator for workplace health and safety. It prevents work-related death, injury and ill health. HSE is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Work and Pensions ." .
